He's waiting in the backyard.

685
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:08,960
Go tell His Highness.

686
00:40:21,850 --> 00:40:23,760
Miss Chudong, why did you come alone?

687
00:40:24,525 --> 00:40:25,475
Where's Uncle Wang?

688
