716
00:41:32,250 --> 00:41:33,039
Exactly.

717
00:41:33,450 --> 00:41:34,840
Everyone in Qingzhou knows

718
00:41:34,975 --> 00:41:37,700
Lord of Jing'an treats
Consort Pei Nanwei as a treasure.

