723
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:49,200
Now, Pei Nanwei is his consort.

724
00:41:52,325 --> 00:41:53,440
I see.

725
00:41:54,100 --> 00:41:54,850
Hey.

726
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,675
Would you like to go
and meet Lord of Jing'an?

727
